s the mouse''s process to the window''s PROCESS prop.  The culprit is ACTIVEEDITW in SETDEDITMAP in DEDITRESHAPEFN.''	Bill''-----''Date': 14 May 84 09':55 PDT'From': Sheil.pa'Subject': Re': tty in mouse process still in latest loadup'In-reply-to': MASINTER.PA''s message of 11 MAY 84 22':50 PDT'To': MASINTER.PA'cc': lispsupport.PA, burton.PA, vanmelle.PA''Yes - it''s a known DEdit bug and I havent patched it, so it''s not surprising its still in the current full. (I do have a diagnosis).''Beau'Workaround: Test Case: Edit-By: Sannella.PAEdit-Date: 21-Aug-84 16':51':09